          <p class='first-para'>
            I am grateful to the noble Earl for that. Of course, a fence which is down is no use at all&#x2014;I entirely agree with him. I beg to withdraw the amendment.</p><p>
            Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
