          <p class='first-para'>
            I am glad to accept this amendment made by the noble Lady, Lady Saltoun. There are very strong welfare reasons for the amendment. She is quite right&#x2014;there was some doubt as to just where, in other legislation, this was properly prohibited. We are happy to accept the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
