      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0570P0-02340'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0570P0_19960306_GCR_285' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendment agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0570P0-02341'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0570P0_19960306_GCR_286' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 101 not moved.</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0570P0-02342'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0570P0_19960306_GCR_287' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">The Earl of Lindsay</span> moved Amendments Nos. 102 to 104:
        <q>Page 15, line 20, column 3, at end insert ("and the words "the provisions of this Part of ".").</q>
        <q>Page 15, line 27, column 3, at end insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>("In section 27, in subsection (1), the words "firearm or ammunition, vehicle or boat".").</q>
        <q>Page 15, line 27, column 3, at end insert&#x2014; ("In section 31, subsection (2).").</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0570P0-02343'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0570P0_19960306_GCR_288' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The noble Earl said: I spoke to Amendments Nos. 102 to 104 when speaking to Amendment No. 21. I beg to move.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0570P0-02344'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0570P0_19960306_GCR_289' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendments agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0570P0-02345'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0570P0_19960306_GCR_290' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 2, as amended, agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0570P0-02346'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0570P0_19960306_GCR_291' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Bill to be reported with amendments.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0570P0-02347'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0570P0_19960306_GCR_292' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Committee adjourned at thirteen minutes before seven o'clock.
      </p>
